<FindBugsFilter xmlns="https://github.com/spotbugs/filter/3.0.0">
  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has NONE. The value types are immutable records and the rule classes hold no exposed
    mutable state, so the representation-exposure detectors (EI_EXPOSE_REP / EI_EXPOSE_REP2) stay quiet
    without any suppression. The filter is kept (empty) so a future, genuinely-reviewed suppression has
    a home with a reason, rather than being added inline.
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
